*美國[[漫畫家|漫畫家]][[索爾·斯坦伯格|索爾·斯坦伯格]]曾服役於中美合作所，以漫畫為盟軍作宣傳。<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://intellit.muskingum.edu/wwii_folder/wwiioss_folder/ossindivlsa-h.html | title=WORLD WAR II OSS Individuals | publisher=Muskingum University | access-date=2015-05-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150525202916/http://intellit.muskingum.edu/wwii_folder/wwiioss_folder/ossindivlsa-h.html | archive-date=2015-05-25 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Bair2012">{{cite book|author=Deirdre Bair|title=''Saul Steinberg: A Biography''|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ZImBfC0-xnwC&pg=PT160|date=20 November 2012|publisher=Knopf Doubleday Publishing Group|isbn=978-0-385-53498-7|pages=159-160}}</ref>

